WITH SOMETHING.

475
00:27:31,350 --> 00:27:32,883
-OH, MY GOODNESS.

476
00:27:32,885 --> 00:27:35,686
YOU REALLY ARE A DUMB BLANQUITA,
AREN'T YOU?

477
00:27:35,688 --> 00:27:36,954
-FUCK YOU.

478
00:27:36,956 --> 00:27:39,423
-TIRED, HUNGRY,
AND NOW VERY GRUMPY.

479
00:27:39,425 --> 00:27:42,893
HUH. LET ME SEE.

480
00:27:49,868 --> 00:27:51,669
-[ SIGHS ]
-THANK YOU.

481
00:27:51,671 --> 00:27:54,104
-GOOD LORD.

482
00:27:54,106 --> 00:27:56,874
[ WATER DRIPPING ]

483
00:28:11,222 --> 00:28:13,757
[ DOOR CHIMES ]

484
00:28:19,130 --> 00:28:21,432
-I'LL TAKE THREE OF THOSE, TOO.

485
00:28:21,434 --> 00:28:23,901
-SURE THING.

486
00:28:23,903 --> 00:28:25,836
[ PAPER RIPS ]

487
00:28:25,838 --> 00:28:27,304
HERE YOU GO.

488
00:28:27,306 --> 00:28:29,807
[ HORN HONKS IN DISTANCE ]

489
00:28:31,810 --> 00:28:35,012
[ CASH REGISTER BEEPING ]

490
00:28:40,919 --> 00:28:42,986
-[ SIGHS ]

491
00:28:42,988 --> 00:28:44,922
[ CASH REGISTER WHIRS ]

492
00:28:44,924 --> 00:28:48,158
THAT'S $9.72.

493
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:52,329
-[ CLEARS THROAT ]

494
00:28:52,331 --> 00:28:54,498
-[ SIGHS ]

495
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:56,800
[ SCRATCHING ]

496
00:28:56,802 --> 00:29:00,804
I'M SORRY, MA'AM, BUT YOU'RE
GONNA HAVE TO HURRY ON UP.

497
00:29:00,806 --> 00:29:02,840
[ SCRATCHING CONTINUES ]

498
00:29:07,479 --> 00:29:10,147
[ SOFT MUSIC PLAYS ]

499
00:29:30,869 --> 00:29:33,003
[ SCRATCHING CONTINUES ]

500
00:29:50,155 --> 00:29:52,189
-OH, GOOD MORNING, LADIES.

501
00:29:54,492 --> 00:29:57,294
LOOKING MIGHTY FINE TODAY.

502
00:30:00,365 --> 00:30:04,234
HONEY BUNS, WHY DON'T YOU AND ME
STEP IN THE OFFICE?

503
00:30:04,236 --> 00:30:06,970
[ WATER SPLASHING,
BUCKET ROLLING ]

504
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:19,216
[ VEHICLE APPROACHES,
HIP-HOP MUSIC PLAYS ]

505
00:30:30,028 --> 00:30:32,963
[ HIP-HOP MUSIC CONTINUES ]

506
00:30:32,965 --> 00:30:34,598
-ARE YOU MESSING WITH ME?!

507
00:30:34,600 --> 00:30:36,600
-BITCH!

508
00:30:36,602 --> 00:30:40,003
I CAN SMELL YOUR PUSSY
THROUGH THE WINDOW.

509
00:30:40,005 --> 00:30:42,172
-FUCK YOU!

510
00:30:42,174 --> 00:30:43,507
[ MUSIC SHUTS OFF ]

511
00:30:46,077 --> 00:30:48,245
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

512
00:30:51,249 --> 00:30:53,951
TELL YOUR DADDY TO BEHAVE,

513
00:30:53,953 --> 00:30:55,552
'CAUSE HE'S ACTING UP,
AND I'M ABOUT --

514
00:30:55,554 --> 00:30:57,221
-HE DON'T LISTEN.

515
00:30:58,489 --> 00:31:00,524
HA HA!

516
00:31:00,526 --> 00:31:02,492
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

517
00:31:02,494 --> 00:31:03,961
BYE, MISSY!

518
00:31:06,364 --> 00:31:07,965
-BYE, KYLE.

519
00:31:07,967 --> 00:31:10,133
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

520
00:31:14,939 --> 00:31:18,475
-HOW'D IT GO TODAY?

521
00:31:18,477 --> 00:31:21,345
-IT'S OKAY.

522
00:31:21,347 --> 00:31:24,047
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC
PLAYS ON RADIO ]

523
00:31:26,351 --> 00:31:29,353
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

524
00:31:29,355 --> 00:31:33,290
JUSTIN'S STALKING ME AGAIN.

525
00:31:33,292 --> 00:31:34,892
-WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

526
00:31:34,894 --> 00:31:38,061
-HE KEEPS COMING IN THE STORE.

527
00:31:38,063 --> 00:31:39,429
-WHY?

528
00:31:39,431 --> 00:31:41,265
-I DON'T KNOW WHY.

529
00:31:41,267 --> 00:31:43,200
-I'M GONNA KILL HIM, MELISSA.

530
00:31:43,202 --> 00:31:45,936
THIS TIME,
I'M GONNA FREAKIN' KILL HIM.

531
00:31:45,938 --> 00:31:47,671
-DON'T BE STUPID.

532
00:31:47,673 --> 00:31:51,275
MOM'S PROBABLY EGGING HIM ON,
KNOWING HER.

533
00:31:51,277 --> 00:31:53,911
-YOUR MOTHER
IS AN ALCOHOLIC BITCH.

534
00:31:53,913 --> 00:31:57,514
-LOOK WHO'S TALKING.

535
00:31:57,516 --> 00:31:58,916
-YEAH.

536
00:31:58,918 --> 00:32:00,684
YOU STILL LOVE HIM.

537
00:32:00,686 --> 00:32:03,153
THAT'S WHY HE'S STALKING YOU,
'CAUSE HE'S IN LOVE WITH YOU.

538
00:32:03,155 --> 00:32:04,922
AND HE WOULDN'T BE
IN LOVE WITH YOU

539
00:32:04,924 --> 00:32:06,690
IF YOU WEREN'T IN LOVE
WITH HIM, TOO!

540
00:32:06,692 --> 00:32:08,392
-WHAT?!

541
00:32:12,297 --> 00:32:14,498
-I SAID IT.

542
00:32:17,101 --> 00:32:20,070
'CAUSE I KNOW IT TO BE A FACT.

543
00:32:23,007 --> 00:32:24,708
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

544
00:32:24,710 --> 00:32:27,010
I HATE THAT GUY.

545
00:32:27,012 --> 00:32:30,380
I HEAR HIS NAME,
AND IT GETS ME NUTS.

546
00:32:30,382 --> 00:32:33,617
I SWEAR TO GOD, THAT GUY --
I...

547
00:32:54,005 --> 00:32:55,572
-WHAT'S THE PRICE?

548
00:33:09,454 --> 00:33:11,288
-HEY.

549
00:33:11,290 --> 00:33:14,157
THIS IS PERFECT FOR YOU.
MAYBE YOU'LL LEARN SOMETHING.

550
00:33:14,159 --> 00:33:15,625
-[ CHUCKLES ]

551
00:33:15,627 --> 00:33:17,294
-I RECKON YOU'D BETTER
CLEAN UP YOUR ACT

552
00:33:17,296 --> 00:33:18,595
IF YOU'RE GONNA BE A DADDY.

553
00:33:18,597 --> 00:33:21,531
LOOK.

554
00:33:21,533 --> 00:33:23,367
IT'S BRAND-NEW,
STILL GOT THE TAGS ON IT.

555
00:33:23,369 --> 00:33:25,202
-WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

556
00:33:25,204 --> 00:33:28,505
-WELL, IT'S TOO SOON TO KNOW
IF IT'S A BOY OR A GIRL,

557
00:33:28,507 --> 00:33:32,109
BUT I THINK IT'S SO CUTE WE
SHOULD BUY IT JUST IN CASE.

558
00:33:32,111 --> 00:33:34,144
I'm pregnant.

559
00:33:34,146 --> 00:33:37,314
[ LAUGHS ]

560
00:33:37,316 --> 00:33:39,583
-YEAH.

561
00:33:39,585 --> 00:33:41,551
YEAH!
-[ LAUGHS ]

562
00:33:41,553 --> 00:33:43,220
-COME HERE!

563
00:33:46,624 --> 00:33:49,092
BIG PAPA.

564
00:33:49,094 --> 00:33:51,728
BIG PAPA IN THE HOUSE!

565
00:33:51,730 --> 00:33:54,364
YOU KNOW IT!

566
00:33:54,366 --> 00:33:56,566
-YOU LIKE IT?

567
00:33:56,568 --> 00:33:58,168
-WELL, MAYBE IT'S NOT --

568
00:33:58,170 --> 00:33:59,770
I WOULDN'T HAVE <i>MY</i> SON
WEARING THAT.

569
00:33:59,772 --> 00:34:01,171
-[ LAUGHS ]

570
00:34:01,173 --> 00:34:04,441
-OH! OH! OH!

571
00:34:04,443 --> 00:34:08,478
-I HAVE TO CHECK AND SEE IF THEY
HAVE A DAYCARE AT COLLEGE.

572
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:10,580
-NO WAY, MELISSA.

573
00:34:10,582 --> 00:34:13,216
<i>I'M</i> TAKING CARE
OF THE LITTLE GUY.

574
00:34:13,218 --> 00:34:14,785
-[ CHUCKLES ]

575
00:34:14,787 --> 00:34:17,254
-I'M GONNA MAKE
AN AWESOME DADDY.

576
00:34:17,256 --> 00:34:19,456
-YOU WILL, INDEED.

577
00:34:19,458 --> 00:34:25,128
-YOU KNOW,
I GOT SOME POWERFUL SPERM.

578
00:34:25,130 --> 00:34:26,663
-[ LAUGHS ]

579
00:34:26,665 --> 00:34:28,598
YEP. SURE DO.

580
00:34:28,600 --> 00:34:30,400
I THOUGHT YOU COULDN'T MAKE
NO BABIES.

581
00:34:30,402 --> 00:34:32,536
-WELL...

582
00:34:32,538 --> 00:34:36,073
-I WANT A LITTLE GIRL.

583
00:34:36,075 --> 00:34:40,110
I WANT TO DRESS UP
A LITTLE GIRL <i>SO BAD.</i>

584
00:34:40,112 --> 00:34:42,646
[ CRUNCHING ]

585
00:34:42,648 --> 00:34:45,282
[ CHUCKLES ]

586
00:34:45,284 --> 00:34:47,684
-LISTEN, I WANT
TO ASK YOU SOMETHING,

587
00:34:47,686 --> 00:34:50,220
AND I WANT YOU
TO TELL ME THE TRUTH.

588
00:34:50,222 --> 00:34:54,591
DID YOU EVER GET PREGNANT
WITH JUSTIN?

589
00:34:54,593 --> 00:34:58,195
-WE ALREADY TALKED ABOUT THAT.

590
00:34:58,197 --> 00:35:01,131
REMEMBER?

591
00:35:01,133 --> 00:35:03,133
-YEAH. OKAY.

592
00:35:03,135 --> 00:35:05,602
OKAY, BUT, UH...

593
00:35:05,604 --> 00:35:09,806
DID -- DID YOU <i>WANT</i> TO HAVE
A BABY WITH HIM?

594
00:35:09,808 --> 00:35:12,843
I'M NOT GONNA GET MAD.

595
00:35:12,845 --> 00:35:14,878
-HE HAD KYLE.

596
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:16,413
THAT WAS ENOUGH.

597
00:35:16,415 --> 00:35:19,249
-I'M NOT TALKING
ABOUT THAT DICK HEAD'S KID.

598
00:35:19,251 --> 00:35:22,686
-LOOK, KYLE -- HE DON'T HAVE
NOTHING TO DO WITH JUSTIN.

599
00:35:22,688 --> 00:35:26,756
-YEAH, AND HE DON'T HAVE NOTHING
TO DO WITH YOU OR US, EITHER.

600
00:35:28,793 --> 00:35:32,295
-YEAH. THAT'S TRUE.

601
00:35:36,701 --> 00:35:38,568
-ALL RIGHT.

602
00:35:38,570 --> 00:35:41,171
SO, UH...

603
00:35:41,173 --> 00:35:43,306
WELL, LET'S GET MARRIED, HUH?

604
00:35:50,915 --> 00:35:54,317
-ARE YOU...

605
00:35:54,319 --> 00:35:56,219
ARE YOU ASKING ME?

606
00:35:56,221 --> 00:35:57,821
-YEAH.

607
00:35:57,823 --> 00:35:59,723
-WELL...

608
00:35:59,725 --> 00:36:02,926
-OH.

609
00:36:02,928 --> 00:36:05,595
OKAY.

610
00:36:05,597 --> 00:36:07,230
-[ LAUGHS ]

611
00:36:09,333 --> 00:36:11,601
-MELISSA?

612
00:36:11,603 --> 00:36:12,936
-MM-HMM?

613
00:36:12,938 --> 00:36:14,938
-WOULD YOU MARRY ME?

614
00:36:17,909 --> 00:36:20,810
-HMM. ALL RIGHT.

615
00:36:20,812 --> 00:36:23,647
-WHAT TOOK YOU SO LONG
TO ANSWER THE QUESTION?

616
00:36:23,649 --> 00:36:25,949
-[ LAUGHS ]

617
00:36:25,951 --> 00:36:27,817
-OKAY.

618
00:36:27,819 --> 00:36:29,719
COME ON. WE'RE IN A RESTAURANT.
CUT IT OUT.

619
00:36:29,721 --> 00:36:32,389
-[ LAUGHS ]

620
00:36:32,391 --> 00:36:34,824
-HEY! STOP IT.

621
00:36:34,826 --> 00:36:37,527
-CAN YOU -- CAN YOU WAIT
TILL WE GET BACK HOME?

622
00:36:37,529 --> 00:36:40,230
-[ LAUGHS ]

623
00:36:40,232 --> 00:36:41,498
-I LOVE YOU.

624
00:36:41,500 --> 00:36:42,866
-I LOVE YOU, TOO.

625
00:36:42,868 --> 00:36:45,569
-I MEAN IT.
I REALLY LOVE YOU.

626
00:37:01,552 --> 00:37:02,953
[ ENGINE SHUTS OFF ]

627
00:37:05,856 --> 00:37:08,258
COME HERE.

628
00:37:16,901 --> 00:37:20,570
SO, YOU THINK I CAN MAKE
AN HONEST WOMAN OUT OF YOU?

629
00:37:20,572 --> 00:37:21,871
YEAH?

630
00:37:21,873 --> 00:37:23,940
-I'VE BEEN A BAD GIRL.

631
00:37:23,942 --> 00:37:25,408
-YEAH. YOU REALLY HAVE BEEN.

632
00:37:25,410 --> 00:37:26,977
-OH, YEAH.

633
00:37:26,979 --> 00:37:28,511
-AND YOU'RE GONNA BE...

634
00:37:28,513 --> 00:37:30,547
AN EVEN WORSE GIRL
IN ABOUT TWO MINUTES.

635
00:37:30,549 --> 00:37:32,415
-[ LAUGHS ]

636
00:37:32,417 --> 00:37:34,551
-WAIT A MINUTE.
YOU MADE ME MISS THE ROOM.

637
00:37:34,553 --> 00:37:36,353
-RIGHT HERE.

638
00:37:36,355 --> 00:37:37,654
-[ SIGHS ]

639
00:37:37,656 --> 00:37:39,022
[ ARGUING IN DISTANCE ]

640
00:37:39,024 --> 00:37:41,658
[ MOANING ]

641
00:37:45,830 --> 00:37:47,330
-OH!

642
00:37:47,332 --> 00:37:49,466
COME ON, NOW. WAIT.

643
00:37:49,468 --> 00:37:51,801
COME AND GET IT, BABY.

644
00:37:59,443 --> 00:38:03,013
[ RADIO CHATTER ]

645
00:38:03,015 --> 00:38:05,582
-HERE.

646
00:38:05,584 --> 00:38:06,850
-NO, IT'S OKAY.

647
00:38:06,852 --> 00:38:09,953
-IT'S NOT FOR YOU.
IT'S FOR THE BABY.

648
00:38:09,955 --> 00:38:11,855
HMM?

649
00:38:14,692 --> 00:38:17,360
-WELL, IF YOU SAY IT LIKE THAT.

650
00:38:19,330 --> 00:38:21,364
<i>-...CLOUD COMFORT</i>
<i>PILLOW-TOP BED.</i>

651
00:38:21,366 --> 00:38:24,768
<i>SERENITY AWAITS</i>
<i>AT BOCA BEACH CLUB SPA,</i>

652
00:38:24,770 --> 00:38:27,404
<i>NEAR CLEARWATER BEACH.</i>

653
00:38:27,406 --> 00:38:29,572
-$5.53 IS YOUR CHANGE.

654
00:38:29,574 --> 00:38:30,774
YOU SURE YOU DON'T WANT A BAG?

655
00:38:30,776 --> 00:38:32,442
-NO, THANKS.
HAVE A GOOD ONE.

656
00:38:32,444 --> 00:38:33,943
-ALL RIGHT. WELL, THANKS
FOR SHOPPING AT SUNLIGHT JR.

657
00:38:33,945 --> 00:38:35,445
[ CHATTERING IN DISTANCE ]

658
00:38:35,447 --> 00:38:37,047
HEY, HELEN. HOW ARE YA?

659
00:38:37,049 --> 00:38:38,448
MELISSA?

660
00:38:38,450 --> 00:38:39,649
-YEP?

661
00:38:39,651 --> 00:38:43,453
-THIS HERE IS HELEN McCORMICK.

662
00:38:43,455 --> 00:38:44,754
-OH.

663
00:38:44,756 --> 00:38:47,624
HI.

664
00:38:47,626 --> 00:38:49,793
YOU THE LADY
FROM THE COLLEGE PROGRAM?

665
00:38:49,795 --> 00:38:52,028
-[ CHUCKLES POLITELY ]
NICE TO MEET YOU.

666
00:38:52,030 --> 00:38:54,564
-NO, SHE'S, UH,
GONNA GIVE YOU A DRUG TEST.

667
00:38:54,566 --> 00:38:57,534
-OH. DIDN'T I DO
ONE OF THEM ALREADY?

668
00:38:57,536 --> 00:39:00,537
-YES.
WHAT, ARE YOU WORRIED?

669
00:39:00,539 --> 00:39:02,939
-HELL NO.

670
00:39:02,941 --> 00:39:06,576
I DON'T DO NO DRUGS!

671
00:39:06,578 --> 00:39:08,511
COME ON. LET'S DO THIS.

672
00:39:10,548 --> 00:39:12,549
-HEY, LITTLE MAN.
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YA?

673
00:39:12,551 --> 00:39:13,850
[ DOOR CHIMES ]

674
00:39:13,852 --> 00:39:15,118
A BALL, HUH?

675
00:39:49,153 --> 00:39:51,521
[ ENGINE SHUTS OFF ]

676
00:39:51,523 --> 00:39:53,757
[ DOG BARKS IN DISTANCE ]

677
00:40:21,786 --> 00:40:24,687
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

678
00:40:29,427 --> 00:40:31,694
-WHY, RICHIE.
WHAT A PLEASANT SURPRISE.

679
00:40:31,696 --> 00:40:33,196
-YEAH.

680
00:40:33,198 --> 00:40:35,965
-AND HOW IN THE WORLD
IS MY BEAUTIFUL DAUGHTER?

681
00:40:35,967 --> 00:40:37,867
-SHE'S GOOD.
SHE'S REAL GOOD.

682
00:40:37,869 --> 00:40:40,203
-YEAH, TOO GOOD TO COME
AND SEE HER MAMA?

683
00:40:40,205 --> 00:40:42,172
-NO, I MEAN,
SHE'S WORKING ALL THE TIME.

684
00:40:42,174 --> 00:40:43,640
YOU KNOW HOW THAT IS.

685
00:40:43,642 --> 00:40:44,908
-OH, YEAH. AT SUNSET JR.?

686
00:40:44,910 --> 00:40:46,743
-YEAH, "SUNLIGHT."
-WHATEVER.

687
00:40:51,782 --> 00:40:53,850
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

688
00:40:58,756 --> 00:41:01,591
-PUT YOUR CUP IN HERE, PLEASE.

689
00:41:07,164 --> 00:41:10,467
CAN YOU STRAIGHTEN UP IN HERE?

690
00:41:10,469 --> 00:41:12,969
THIS PLACE
IS KIND OF DISGUSTING.

691
00:41:12,971 --> 00:41:15,138
-YES, MA'AM.

692
00:41:25,916 --> 00:41:28,151
[ SPRAYING ]

693
00:41:28,153 --> 00:41:30,653
-NO! NUH-UH! NO!

694
00:41:30,655 --> 00:41:34,858
-HOW DID YOU KNOW THAT
FAMILY SERVICES WROTE ME UP

695
00:41:34,860 --> 00:41:37,060
FOR NOT HAVING ENOUGH FOOD
IN MY CUPBOARD?

696
00:41:37,062 --> 00:41:38,628
- NO! [ CRIES ]

697
00:41:38,630 --> 00:41:40,530
-I'M SORRY TO HEAR THAT.

698
00:41:40,532 --> 00:41:42,599
-OH, DON'T BE.
IT'S NOT THEIR FAULT.

699
00:41:42,601 --> 00:41:44,634
THEY THINK THEY'RE DOING
THEIR JOB,

700
00:41:44,636 --> 00:41:47,737
BUT THEY KNOW THAT FOSTER CARE
DOESN'T GIVE ME ENOUGH MONEY

701
00:41:47,739 --> 00:41:49,239
TO FEED ALL THESE DAMN KIDS.

702
00:41:51,609 --> 00:41:53,843
-YOU STOP IT!

703
00:41:53,845 --> 00:41:56,279
-DID YOU GET THIS
AT THE FOOD BANK?

704
00:41:56,281 --> 00:41:57,747
-YES, MA'AM.

705
00:41:57,749 --> 00:41:59,082
[ BAG RUSTLES ]

706
00:41:59,084 --> 00:42:00,783
-CRAP.

707
00:42:00,785 --> 00:42:02,919
THEY'RE NOT GIVING OUT
ANY MORE PEANUT BUTTER,

708
00:42:02,921 --> 00:42:04,921
AND THAT'S ALL JERAL WILL EAT.

709
00:42:04,923 --> 00:42:07,190
I DON'T KNOW HOW
I'M GONNA FEED THAT BOY.

710
00:42:07,192 --> 00:42:09,259
ARE YOU STAYIN'?

711
00:42:09,261 --> 00:42:11,961
-LISTEN, I WANT TO TALK
TO YOU ABOUT JUSTIN.

712
00:42:11,963 --> 00:42:14,097
HE'S BEEN HASSLING
MELISSA AGAIN.

713
00:42:14,099 --> 00:42:17,667
HE'S BEEN SHOWING UP AT HER JOB,
YOU KNOW, SHIT LIKE THAT.

714
00:42:17,669 --> 00:42:19,869
-WELL, THAT'S BECAUSE
THE RESTRAINING ORDER'S UP.

715
00:42:19,871 --> 00:42:23,172
-WELL, I'LL JUST GET MY 9

716
00:42:23,174 --> 00:42:25,742
AND SETTLE IT
THE OLD-FASHIONED WAY.

717
00:42:25,744 --> 00:42:27,076
BOOM!

718
00:42:27,078 --> 00:42:28,878
-YOU KNOW HIS MAMA DIED.

719
00:42:28,880 --> 00:42:31,915
-YEAH? SORRY TO HEAR THAT.
SHIT HAPPENS.

720
00:42:31,917 --> 00:42:34,117
-YEAH, BUT I GOT TO PAY JUSTIN
MY RENT NOW.

721
00:42:34,119 --> 00:42:36,653
THAT MAKES HIM MY LANDLORD.

722
00:42:36,655 --> 00:42:37,887
-WHOA!

723
00:42:37,889 --> 00:42:39,088
-OH!

724
00:42:39,090 --> 00:42:40,323
YOU WANT A MOTORBOAT RIDE?

725
00:42:40,325 --> 00:42:41,891
-YES.
-ALL RIGHT.

726
00:42:41,893 --> 00:42:45,595
♪ MOTORBOAT, MOTORBOAT

727
00:42:45,597 --> 00:42:48,197
♪ GOES SO SLOW

728
00:42:48,199 --> 00:42:50,934
♪ MOTORBOAT, MOTORBOAT
GOES SO FAST ♪

729
00:42:50,936 --> 00:42:53,903
♪ MOTORBOAT, MOTORBOAT,
STEP ON THE GAS! ♪

730
00:42:53,905 --> 00:42:55,738
[ IMITATES ENGINE REVVING ]

731
00:42:55,740 --> 00:42:57,740
-SAM. COME HERE.

732
00:42:57,742 --> 00:42:59,342
LISTEN, I WANT YOU
TO GO TELL THE OTHER KIDS

733
00:42:59,344 --> 00:43:01,244
WE'RE GONNA HAVE NOODLES.

734
00:43:01,246 --> 00:43:05,748
THEY CAN HAVE NOODLES IN BUTTER
OR COTTAGE CHEESE OR KETCHUP.

735
00:43:05,750 --> 00:43:07,150
YOU FIND OUT WHAT THEY WANT,

736
00:43:07,152 --> 00:43:09,085
AND YOU COME TELL KATHLEEN,
OKAY?

737
00:43:09,087 --> 00:43:10,587
-YES, MOM.

738
00:43:10,589 --> 00:43:12,288
-I WIN! I WIN!
-OH, THAT'S GREAT.

739
00:43:12,290 --> 00:43:15,024
WHY DON'T YOU TAKE HER OVER
THERE TO PLAY, CODY?

740
00:43:16,727 --> 00:43:20,830
KIDS -- GIVE THEM AN INCH,
THEY'LL TAKE A MILE.

741
00:43:20,832 --> 00:43:22,765
-YEAH, I WOULDN'T KNOW.

742
00:43:31,842 --> 00:43:33,242
[ DOOR BEEPS ]

743
00:43:39,149 --> 00:43:41,317
-HELLO.

744
00:43:41,319 --> 00:43:42,719
HEY, PUMPKIN.

745
00:43:42,721 --> 00:43:44,354
OOH, LOOK AT YOU.

746
00:43:44,356 --> 00:43:45,888
-OH, SHE LIKES YOU.

747
00:43:45,890 --> 00:43:47,357
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

748
00:43:47,359 --> 00:43:49,959
YOU WANT HER?

749
00:43:49,961 --> 00:43:53,763
-WELL, I'M ABOUT READY
TO HAVE MY OWN, SO...

750
00:43:53,765 --> 00:43:56,332
-OH, WELL, GOOD LUCK --
OR CONGRATULATIONS...

751
00:43:56,334 --> 00:43:58,134
I GUESS.

752
00:43:58,136 --> 00:44:00,303
[ BABY FUSSING ]

753
00:44:00,305 --> 00:44:02,705
[ SOFT MUSIC PLAYS ]

754
00:44:05,876 --> 00:44:08,311
[ BIRD SHRIEKS ]

755
00:44:08,313 --> 00:44:10,113
-WHAT ABOUT ZEKE?

756
00:44:10,115 --> 00:44:11,781
YOU LIKE ZEKE?

757
00:44:11,783 --> 00:44:15,118
-YEAH, I DO.
IT'S CUTE.

758
00:44:15,120 --> 00:44:17,887
I LIKE "Z" NAMES.

759
00:44:17,889 --> 00:44:20,690
LIKE...

760
00:44:20,692 --> 00:44:23,426
ZARA OR ZORA.

761
00:44:23,428 --> 00:44:25,695
YOU LIKE ZORA?

762
00:44:25,697 --> 00:44:27,196
-ZORA?

763
00:44:27,198 --> 00:44:28,931
-MM-HMM.

764
00:44:28,933 --> 00:44:31,034
-YOU FREAKIN' KIDDING ME?

765
00:44:31,036 --> 00:44:32,902
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

766
00:44:32,904 --> 00:44:34,704
THAT SOUNDS LIKE A WITCH.

767
00:44:34,706 --> 00:44:37,040
OR A STRIPPER.

768
00:44:37,042 --> 00:44:39,809
-OR BOTH -- A STRIPPER WITCH.

769
00:44:39,811 --> 00:44:41,878
-NO.

770
00:44:41,880 --> 00:44:45,181
MY DAUGHTER'S GONNA BE
AN ASS KICKER LIKE HER MAMA.

771
00:44:45,183 --> 00:44:48,451
YEAH.

772
00:44:50,287 --> 00:44:53,890
-I LIKE OLD-FASHIONED NAMES,
TOO, LIKE...

773
00:44:53,892 --> 00:44:56,926
LIKE JAMIE. JAMIE.

774
00:44:56,928 --> 00:44:59,796
SHE COULD BE A BOY OR A GIRL.

775
00:44:59,798 --> 00:45:03,399
-YEAH, JAMIE'S ALL RIGHT.

776
00:45:03,401 --> 00:45:05,768
IT'S NOT SPECIAL, THOUGH.

777
00:45:05,770 --> 00:45:09,072
WHAT ABOUT, UM...

778
00:45:09,074 --> 00:45:13,443
WHAT ABOUT CHESTER?

779
00:45:13,445 --> 00:45:16,212
NO?

780
00:45:16,214 --> 00:45:21,718
-HOW COME YOU ALWAYS THINK
OF BOYS' NAMES, HMM?

781
00:45:21,720 --> 00:45:25,021
ARE YOU GONNA LOVE THIS BABY
IF IT'S A GIRL?

782
00:45:25,023 --> 00:45:28,958
-UM, WHAT DO <i>YOU</i> THINK?

783
00:45:28,960 --> 00:45:33,496
DO YOU THINK I WOULDN'T LOVE
THE BABY IF IT WAS A GIRL?

784
00:45:33,498 --> 00:45:36,065
COME ON, LADY.

785
00:45:36,067 --> 00:45:38,167
WHO ARE YOU TALKING TO?

786
00:45:38,169 --> 00:45:42,205
-MY DAD DIDN'T GIVE
A FLYING FUCK ABOUT ME.

787
00:45:42,207 --> 00:45:46,809
-WELL, I'M NOT YOUR DAD.

788
00:45:46,811 --> 00:45:48,311
I'M YOUR DADDY.

789
00:45:48,313 --> 00:45:51,214
-RICH, THEY'RE SORE.
DON'T TOUCH.

790
00:45:51,216 --> 00:45:55,051
OW! [ Laughing ] OW!

791
00:45:55,053 --> 00:45:59,856
HOW COME YOU'RE ALWAYS SO HORNY
ALL THE TIME, HUH?

792
00:45:59,858 --> 00:46:03,426
YOU ACT LIKE I NEVER FUCK YOU.

793
00:46:09,366 --> 00:46:12,034
SO, I WAS THINKING,

794
00:46:12,036 --> 00:46:15,538
SO I CAN GET ALL THOSE EXTRA
HOURS YOU WERE TALKING ABOUT,

795
00:46:15,540 --> 00:46:19,008
CAN I WORK A COUPLE EXTRA SHIFTS
A WEEK FOR A WHILE?

796
00:46:19,010 --> 00:46:21,244
-WELL, FUNNY
YOU SHOULD SAY THAT, MEL.

797
00:46:21,246 --> 00:46:24,480
STARTING NEXT WEEK, I'M GONNA
HAVE TO PUT YOU ON GRAVEYARD.

798
00:46:24,482 --> 00:46:26,883
YOU CAN STILL WORK MORNINGS
IF YOU WANT TO,

799
00:46:26,885 --> 00:46:29,819
BUT I'M GONNA HAVE TO SWITCH
YOUR SHIFT OVER TO GRAVEYARD.

800
00:46:29,821 --> 00:46:32,054
-WHAT?

801
00:46:32,056 --> 00:46:34,824
WHERE'S VIVIAN?
SHE DOES GRAVEYARD.

802
00:46:34,826 --> 00:46:37,527
-SHE <i>DID</i> GRAVEYARD.

803
00:46:37,529 --> 00:46:39,428
VIVIAN QUIT.

804
00:46:39,430 --> 00:46:41,798
-WELL, <i>I</i> CAN'T DO IT.

805
00:46:41,800 --> 00:46:44,934
I'M GONNA GET ROBBED OR RAPED
OR SOMETHING.

806
00:46:44,936 --> 00:46:46,969
WHY CAN'T <i>YOU</i> DO IT?

807
00:46:46,971 --> 00:46:48,938
-'CAUSE I'M
THE ASSISTANT MANAGER,

808
00:46:48,940 --> 00:46:50,439
AND YOU'RE THE CASHIER.

809
00:46:50,441 --> 00:46:53,075
NOW, YOU WANT TO GO TRAIN
TO BE AN ASSISTANT MANAGER,

810
00:46:53,077 --> 00:46:54,443
THEN YOU TELL <i>ME</i> WHAT TO DO.

811
00:46:54,445 --> 00:46:55,978
UNTIL THEN,
I'LL TELL <i>YOU</i> WHAT TO DO.

812
00:46:55,980 --> 00:46:57,180
WE CLEAR?

813
00:46:57,182 --> 00:47:00,416
-WHY'D SHE QUIT?
-I DON'T KNOW.

814
00:47:00,418 --> 00:47:01,984
CALLED ME ON THE PHONE.

815
00:47:01,986 --> 00:47:04,921
SHE SAID SHE DIDN'T WANT
TO WORK HERE NO MORE.

816
00:47:04,923 --> 00:47:07,857
MAYBE SHE WANTS TO BE
A DRUG DEALER.

817
00:47:07,859 --> 00:47:09,525
-OH, YEAH?

818
00:47:09,527 --> 00:47:13,162
WELL, MAYBE I'D RATHER SELL
DRUGS THAN WORK THE GRAVEYARD.

819
00:47:13,164 --> 00:47:15,231
GOOD LORD.

820
00:47:15,233 --> 00:47:17,300
[ SIGHS ]

821
00:47:17,302 --> 00:47:19,836
HEY, KELLY.

822
00:47:19,838 --> 00:47:21,037
YOU WANT YOUR SMOKES?

823
00:47:21,039 --> 00:47:23,539
-YEAH. THANKS, MEL.

824
00:47:23,541 --> 00:47:25,174
-SO, CAN I BRING RICHIE?

825
00:47:25,176 --> 00:47:26,542
-SUIT YOURSELF.

826
00:47:26,544 --> 00:47:29,178
JUST DON'T LET ME SEE HIM
BEHIND THE COUNTER.

827
00:47:29,180 --> 00:47:32,315
-ARE YOU GONNA LET ME HAVE
THOSE EXTRA SHIFTS, OR WHAT?

828
00:47:32,317 --> 00:47:35,184
-YEAH, IF YOU CAN HANDLE THEM,
YOU CAN HAVE THEM.

829
00:47:35,186 --> 00:47:36,953
-THANKS.

830
00:47:36,955 --> 00:47:39,222
[ CASH REGISTER BEEPS, WHIRS ]

831
00:47:39,224 --> 00:47:40,590
-THANKS.

832
00:47:40,592 --> 00:47:43,626
-WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

833
00:47:43,628 --> 00:47:47,163
WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?!
THAT'S HER FAMILY!

834
00:47:47,165 --> 00:47:49,198
-SO? SHE DON'T WORK HERE
NO MORE.

835
00:47:49,200 --> 00:47:51,234
WHY SHOULD I
HAVE TO LOOK AT 'EM?

836
00:47:51,236 --> 00:47:54,871
-YOU KNOW, YOU'RE AN ASSHOLE,
YOU KNOW THAT?

837
00:47:54,873 --> 00:47:58,274
-YEAH, WELL, YOU BEST WATCH
YOUR MOUTH, MISS.

838
00:47:58,276 --> 00:48:01,177
-I <i>CAN'T</i> DO THE GRAVEYARD.

839
00:48:01,179 --> 00:48:05,114
-YOU <i>WILL</i> DO THE GRAVEYARD,
OR YOU WON'T HAVE A JOB.

840
00:48:05,116 --> 00:48:08,918
NOW GET BACK TO WORK.
YOU HAVE A CUSTOMER.

841
00:48:11,955 --> 00:48:14,023
[ GULLS CRYING ]

842
00:48:20,330 --> 00:48:25,101
[ SHOUTING IN DISTANCE ]

843
00:48:25,103 --> 00:48:26,636
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

844
00:48:26,638 --> 00:48:28,237
-RICHIE!

845
00:48:28,239 --> 00:48:29,505
-YEP?

846
00:48:29,507 --> 00:48:31,574
-YOU COMING?

847
00:48:31,576 --> 00:48:34,010
-NO, I'M GOOD.

848
00:48:34,012 --> 00:48:35,645
I'M GOOD!

849
00:48:40,584 --> 00:48:42,385
[ BLOWS AIR ]

850
00:48:44,421 --> 00:48:48,190
GOT SOME WORK TO DO HERE.

851
00:49:00,504 --> 00:49:02,538
[ GASPS ]

852
00:49:02,540 --> 00:49:05,041
-27 CENTS IS YOUR CHANGE.

853
00:49:05,043 --> 00:49:06,375
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

854
00:49:06,377 --> 00:49:07,710
-THANK YOU.
-HOW ARE YOU, SIR?

855
00:49:07,712 --> 00:49:10,613
-GET A FULL HOUSE
AND A MONOPOLY.

856
00:49:10,615 --> 00:49:13,015
[ TRUCK HORN BLARES
IN DISTANCE ]

857
00:49:13,017 --> 00:49:15,952
-WHERE THE HELL YOU GOING?

858
00:49:15,954 --> 00:49:17,253
-I'M SORRY.

859
00:49:20,057 --> 00:49:24,260
I'M SORRY.
I'M SICK. REALLY SICK.

860
00:49:26,096 --> 00:49:27,663
-THANK YOU FOR SHOPPING
AT SUNLIGHT JR.

861
00:49:27,665 --> 00:49:29,465
YOU NEED A BAG, SIR?

862
00:49:31,368 --> 00:49:34,603
-CHECK IT OUT.

863
00:49:34,605 --> 00:49:36,639
20 BUCKS.

864
00:49:36,641 --> 00:49:38,741
-WHERE'S THE DVD PLAYER, RICH?

865
00:49:38,743 --> 00:49:40,543
-COME ON, MAN. 20 BUCKS.
YOU CAN SELL IT FOR $40.

866
00:49:40,545 --> 00:49:42,144
-ARE YOU KIDDING?

867
00:49:42,146 --> 00:49:44,013
DUDE, YOU CAN BUY ONE OF THESE
NEW FOR 30 BUCKS!

868
00:49:44,015 --> 00:49:46,382
-[ SCOFFS ] COME ON, MAN.
ALL RIGHT.

869
00:49:46,384 --> 00:49:49,418
GIVE ME 10 BUCKS,
AND YOU CAN SELL IT FOR $20.

870
00:49:49,420 --> 00:49:52,021
-YOU'RE --
-COME ON, MAN! GIVE IT A SPIN.

871
00:49:52,023 --> 00:49:53,656
-YOU'RE KILLING ME, MAN.

872
00:49:53,658 --> 00:49:55,558
-COME ON, MAN.
I'M YOUR FRIEND.

873
00:49:55,560 --> 00:49:57,360
JUST TAKE IT, MAN. TAKE IT.

874
00:49:57,362 --> 00:50:00,162
YOU DON'T WANT IT, NOBODY'S
PUTTING A GUN TO YOUR HEAD.

875
00:50:00,164 --> 00:50:03,399
-[ SCOFFS ]

876
00:50:03,401 --> 00:50:05,568
WE GOT TO WAIT
TILL AFTER HOURS.

877
00:50:05,570 --> 00:50:07,370
-MICK, I DON'T THINK, UH,

878
00:50:07,372 --> 00:50:11,107
THE CLIENTELE'S GONNA MIND
WATCHING A LITTLE PORNOGRAPHY.

879
00:50:11,109 --> 00:50:14,043
-YEAH, AND IN WALKS THE LADY
FROM THE LIQUOR BOARD,

880
00:50:14,045 --> 00:50:15,444
AND I'M SHUT DOWN.

881
00:50:15,446 --> 00:50:18,581
-COME ON, MAN.
I'M JUST MESSING WITH YOU.

882
00:50:18,583 --> 00:50:22,051
[SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY]
THROUGH THE CABLES.

883
00:50:22,053 --> 00:50:23,719
APPRECIATE IT, MAN.
-[ SIGHS ]

884
00:50:23,721 --> 00:50:25,654
-THAT MACHINE'S GONNA WORK
LIKE A GEM.

885
00:50:25,656 --> 00:50:27,156
-DO YOU WANT TO START A TAB?

886
00:50:27,158 --> 00:50:29,158
-YEAH, SURE.

887
00:50:31,294 --> 00:50:34,697
-♪ <i>MAYBE I'VE FORGOTTEN</i>
<i>MY NAME</i> ♪

888
00:50:34,699 --> 00:50:38,434
-HEY, MICKY.
TELL YOU SOMETHING, MAN?

889
00:50:38,436 --> 00:50:41,470
-YES, SIR.

890
00:50:41,472 --> 00:50:44,173
-MELISSA, UH...

891
00:50:44,175 --> 00:50:47,743
TURNS OUT,
SHE'S GONNA HAVE A BABY.

892
00:50:47,745 --> 00:50:51,313
-[ LAUGHS ]

893
00:50:51,315 --> 00:50:52,715
CONGRATULATIONS, PAPA!
-YEAH.

894
00:50:52,717 --> 00:50:54,450
-THAT'S AWESOME, MAN! YEAH!

895
00:50:54,452 --> 00:50:55,751
-HOW MANY KIDS <i>YOU</i> GOT?

896
00:50:55,753 --> 00:50:57,253
-ME? I GOT FOUR.

897
00:50:57,255 --> 00:51:00,156
I GOT THREE BOYS
AND ONE BABY GIRL.

898
00:51:00,158 --> 00:51:01,690
-WOW.

899
00:51:01,692 --> 00:51:04,226
-AND, UH, THEY'RE HELLCATS,
ALL OF THEM.

900
00:51:04,228 --> 00:51:05,795
A MATTER OF FACT,

901
00:51:05,797 --> 00:51:08,831
MY OLDEST BOY BRIAN
JUST HAD A BABY OF HIS OWN.

902
00:51:08,833 --> 00:51:10,466
-GRANDPA?

903
00:51:10,468 --> 00:51:12,201
-WHAT? NO.

904
00:51:12,203 --> 00:51:14,403
-YOUNG MAN LIKE YOURSELF?
-NOT ME. UNH-UNH. UNH-UNH.

905
00:51:14,405 --> 00:51:17,073
MY GRANDSON'S
GONNA CALL ME "CAPTAIN."

906
00:51:17,075 --> 00:51:19,175
-CAPTAIN, HUH?
-YEAH. YEAH.

907
00:51:19,177 --> 00:51:21,811
MAN, I'M TOO YOUNG
TO BE CALLED GRANDPA

908
00:51:21,813 --> 00:51:25,114
OR PAWPAW, OR FUCK THAT, MAN.

909
00:51:25,116 --> 00:51:26,849
-I CAN'T BELIEVE IT, MAN.

910
00:51:26,851 --> 00:51:29,685
THE WHOLE TIME,
I THOUGHT I WAS...

911
00:51:29,687 --> 00:51:32,188
I THOUGHT I WAS SHOOTING BLANKS.

912
00:51:32,190 --> 00:51:33,456
-HEY, LOOK.

913
00:51:33,458 --> 00:51:35,424
THE LORD WORKS
IN MYSTERIOUS WAYS.

914
00:51:35,426 --> 00:51:37,259
-AMEN.

915
00:51:37,261 --> 00:51:39,462
[ LIQUID POURING ]

916
00:51:41,131 --> 00:51:43,165
-IS MY BABY GONNA BE OKAY?

917
00:51:43,167 --> 00:51:45,201
-I CAN'T REALLY SAY.

918
00:51:45,203 --> 00:51:48,270
I'M THE SONOGRAPHER,
NOT THE DOCTOR.

919
00:51:48,272 --> 00:51:50,739
I'M HERE TO TAKE A PICTURE
OF THE UTERUS,

920
00:51:50,741 --> 00:51:54,276
AND WHEN THE DOCTOR COMES IN,
SHE'LL INTERPRET IT FOR YOU.

921
00:51:54,278 --> 00:51:57,179
-OH. ALL RIGHT.

922
00:52:00,150 --> 00:52:02,251
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

923
00:52:02,253 --> 00:52:06,689
-TAKE A FEW DEEP BREATHS
IN AND OUT FOR NOW.

924
00:52:06,691 --> 00:52:09,658
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

925
00:52:09,660 --> 00:52:11,160
-IS THAT IT?

926
00:52:11,162 --> 00:52:13,762
-YES, MA'AM.

927
00:52:13,764 --> 00:52:16,465
THAT'S YOUR BABY.

928
00:52:19,736 --> 00:52:21,704
-I CAN SEE IT.

929
00:52:21,706 --> 00:52:23,539
-MM-HMM.

930
00:52:28,778 --> 00:52:31,680
-OH, THANK GOD.

931
00:52:31,682 --> 00:52:33,716
THANK GOD.

932
00:52:37,888 --> 00:52:39,922
THANK GOD.

933
00:52:45,695 --> 00:52:47,763
THANK YOU.

934
00:52:56,173 --> 00:52:58,274
[ CRICKETS CHIRPING ]

935
00:53:37,847 --> 00:53:39,615
[ CLATTERING ]

936
00:53:39,617 --> 00:53:42,384
-NOT EVEN A FUCKING PHONE CALL?!

937
00:53:42,386 --> 00:53:43,819
HOW STUPID CAN YOU BE?

938
00:53:43,821 --> 00:53:46,388
YOU KNOW HOW MUCH THIS SHIT
IS GONNA COST US?!

939
00:53:46,390 --> 00:53:49,491
-I WAS BLEEDING.
WHAT WAS I SUPPOSED TO DO?

940
00:53:49,493 --> 00:53:51,660
-CALL YOUR FUCKING MAN!

941
00:53:51,662 --> 00:53:53,295
THAT'S WHAT YOU'RE --
-MY PHONE IS SPENT!

942
00:53:53,297 --> 00:53:55,798
-THEN USE THE FUCKING PAY PHONE,
LIKE THE OLD DAYS!

943
00:53:55,800 --> 00:53:59,401
ALL RIGHT.

944
00:53:59,403 --> 00:54:01,003
LOOK, MEL...

945
00:54:01,005 --> 00:54:03,005
DID THEY DO ANYTHING FOR YA?

946
00:54:03,007 --> 00:54:05,441
CAN YOU TELL ME THAT?

947
00:54:05,443 --> 00:54:09,979
DID THEY GIVE YOU ANY PILLS?
CAN YOU TELL ME?

948
00:54:09,981 --> 00:54:11,847
-I GOT VITAMINS.

949
00:54:11,849 --> 00:54:15,684
-YOU GOT VITAMINS?
DID THEY ACTUALLY DO ANYTHING?

950
00:54:15,686 --> 00:54:18,354
-I SAW THE BABY.
IT WAS ALIVE.

951
00:54:18,356 --> 00:54:19,588
ISN'T THAT GOOD NEWS?

952
00:54:19,590 --> 00:54:20,990
-WELL, THAT'S GREAT NEWS,

953
00:54:20,992 --> 00:54:23,726
