996
00:56:45,869 --> 00:56:49,405
-EDWIN PUT ME ON GRAVEYARD.

997
00:56:51,074 --> 00:56:52,875
-[ SCOFFS ]

998
00:56:52,877 --> 00:56:55,878
OH, NICE.

999
00:56:55,880 --> 00:56:57,780
-YEAH.

1000
00:57:03,686 --> 00:57:07,189
-THE WORK MAY AFFECT THE AMOUNT
OF YOUR CHECK,

1001
00:57:07,191 --> 00:57:10,592
HOWEVER, WE DO NOT COUNT
