1004
00:57:15,733 --> 00:57:17,466
WHEN WE FIGURE
YOUR PAYMENT AMOUNT.

1005
00:57:17,468 --> 00:57:19,034
-[ SIGHS ]

1006
00:57:19,036 --> 00:57:21,904
