1015
00:57:42,226 --> 00:57:44,927
<i>AFTER CALLING IT QUITS</i>
<i>FOUR YEARS AGO,</i>

1016
00:57:44,929 --> 00:57:47,696
<i>DEVELOPERS ARE READY</i>
<i>TO MOVE FORWARD</i>

1017
00:57:47,698 --> 00:57:49,665
<i>WITH PLANS FOR THE MALL</i>
<i>AND UNIVERSITY TOWN CENTER</i>

1018
00:57:49,667 --> 00:57:51,533
<i>IN SARASOTA COUNTY.</i>

1019
00:57:51,535 --> 00:57:55,637
<i>...AND MANATEE COUNTY</i>
<i>HENDERSEN DEVELOPMENT COMPANY</i>

1020
00:57:55,639 --> 00:57:58,774
<i>PLAN A $315 MILLION MALL</i>

1021
00:57:58,776 --> 00:58:00,876
<i>SIMILAR TO THE INTERNATIONAL</i>
<i>PLAZA IN TAMPA.</i>

1022
00:58:00,878 --> 00:58:04,213
[ DOOR OPENS ]
-MELISSA WINTERS?!

1023
00:58:04,215 --> 00:58:06,715
