ON GRAVEYARD.

1142
01:04:26,563 --> 01:04:29,197
IT'S BULLSHIT. I'VE BEEN
WORKING HERE EIGHT MONTHS.

1143
01:04:29,199 --> 01:04:30,532
-I'M SICK OF YOUR LIP.

1144
01:04:30,534 --> 01:04:32,133
-OH, YOU'RE SICK OF <i>MY</i> LIP?

1145
01:04:32,135 --> 01:04:33,969
WHAT ABOUT ALL THE NASTY TALK

1146
01:04:33,971 --> 01:04:36,004
I HEAR COMING OUT <i>YOUR</i> MOUTH
ALL FUCKING DAY LONG?!

1147
01:04:36,006 --> 01:04:37,339
I'M OUT OF HERE.

1148
01:04:37,341 --> 01:04:39,574
-HEY, YOU LEAVE,
YOU AIN'T NEVER COMING BACK,

1149
01:04:39,576 --> 01:04:41,443
