YOU GET IT?

1150
01:04:41,445 --> 01:04:43,578
-[ SIGHS ]

1151
01:04:43,580 --> 01:04:45,614
YOU KNOW, I'M WONDERING
IF THEY GOT A CAMERA

1152
01:04:45,616 --> 01:04:47,048
IN THAT WALK-IN,

1153
01:04:47,050 --> 01:04:49,084
TAKING PICTURES OF YOU
JERKING OFF,

1154
01:04:49,086 --> 01:04:50,919
YOU NASTY MAN!
-ALL RIGHT. THAT'S IT.

1155
01:04:50,921 --> 01:04:53,255
OFF THE PREMISES, BOTH OF YOU,
OR I'M GONNA CALL THE COPS!

1156
01:04:53,257 --> 01:04:55,924
GET OFF THE PREMISES RIGHT NOW,
OR I'LL CALL THE COPS ON YOU!

1157
01:04:55,926 --> 01:04:57,926
RIGHT NOW!

1158
01:04:57,928 --> 01:04:59,327
-YOU SHOULD HAVE
WOKE ME UP, RICH.

1159
01:04:59,329 --> 01:05:01,029
NOW LOOK WHAT HAPPENED.
I JUST LOST MY JOB.

1160
01:05:01,031 --> 01:05:02,330
-WAIT A MINUTE.
YOU'RE SAYING IT'S <i>MY</i> FAULT?

1161
01:05:02,332 --> 01:05:04,132
-I'M JUST SAYING
YOU SHOULD HAVE WOKE ME UP

1162
01:05:04,134 --> 01:05:05,634
WHEN CUSTOMERS COME IN!

1163
01:05:05,636 --> 01:05:08,103
-SO YOU'RE BLAMING ME
FOR TRYING TO HELP YOU

1164
01:05:08,105 --> 01:05:09,638
HELP OUR BABY BE HEALTHY?
IS THAT IT?

1165
01:05:09,640 --> 01:05:11,106
COME ON, MEL.

1166
01:05:11,108 --> 01:05:13,041
-SURE AM BLAMING YOU.

1167
01:05:13,043 --> 01:05:14,342
-[ Sighing ] ALL RIGHT.

1168
01:05:14,344 --> 01:05:15,577
-IT'S MY JOB, NOT YOURS!

1169
01:05:15,579 --> 01:05:17,078
-WE'LL FIGURE IT OUT, BABY.

1170
01:05:17,080 --> 01:05:18,513
I'M GONNA TAKE CARE OF YOU,
ALL RIGHT?

1171
01:05:18,515 --> 01:05:19,915
-[ Skeptically ] YEAH.

1172
01:05:19,917 --> 01:05:23,551
-[ SIGHS ]

1173
01:05:36,365 --> 01:05:39,167
-YOU PAY FOR THE NIGHTS
YOU STAY HERE, OKAY?

1174
01:05:39,169 --> 01:05:40,635
THERE'S NO CREDIT.

1175
01:05:40,637 --> 01:05:43,705
-M-M-MY WIFE, SHE CAN MAYBE HELP
CLEAN SOME OF THE ROOMS?

1176
01:05:43,707 --> 01:05:45,373
-[ SCOFFS ] OKAY, YEAH.

1177
01:05:45,375 --> 01:05:47,342
THIS IS A JOB
INTERVIEW NOW, HUH?

1178
01:05:47,344 --> 01:05:49,277
NO. I HAVE A MAID.
SHE'S VERY GOOD.

1179
01:05:49,279 --> 01:05:51,313
IF YOU STAY IN YOUR ROOM
PAST NEXT WEEK,

1180
01:05:51,315 --> 01:05:52,547
I'M CALLING THE POLICE.

1181
01:05:52,549 --> 01:05:54,582
-HEY, HEY, JIMMY.

1182
01:05:54,584 --> 01:05:56,952
I GOT THE RENT, MAN.
-Where's the other credit card?

1183
01:05:56,954 --> 01:05:59,587
-HUH?
-CREDIT CARD?

1184
01:05:59,589 --> 01:06:01,323
-WE GOT RID OF THEM, REMEMBER?

1185
01:06:01,325 --> 01:06:04,225
-HEY, DO YOU GUYS WANT TO STAY
WITH ME AND KRISTI?

1186
01:06:04,227 --> 01:06:05,527
-NO, THANKS.

1187
01:06:05,529 --> 01:06:07,963
-YOU CAN SLEEP
ON THE FLOOR, MAN.

1188
01:06:07,965 --> 01:06:09,297
RICHIE!

1189
01:06:10,967 --> 01:06:13,601
-I THINK I GOT SOMETHING, RICH.

1190
01:06:13,603 --> 01:06:16,004
AW, SHIT.

1191
01:06:16,006 --> 01:06:17,405
[ SIGHS ]

1192
01:06:17,407 --> 01:06:19,674
-HEY, MEL?
-WHAT?

1193
01:06:19,676 --> 01:06:21,743
-THINK ABOUT IT.
IT COULD BE A LOT WORSE.

1194
01:06:21,745 --> 01:06:24,012
WE COULD BE <i>THIS</i> GUY.
-HA HA.

1195
01:06:24,014 --> 01:06:27,082
-KIND OF LOOKS LIKE EDWIN,
THOUGH, DON'T HE?

1196
01:06:27,084 --> 01:06:28,483
[ WATER SPLASHES ]

1197
01:06:28,485 --> 01:06:30,618
-THAT FISH IS <i>WAY</i> CUTER
THAN EDWIN.

1198
01:06:30,620 --> 01:06:32,988
-YEAH.
-TRUST ME.

1199
01:06:44,166 --> 01:06:46,234
-GOD DAMN IT!

1200
01:06:46,236 --> 01:06:48,503
HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU?!

1201
01:06:48,505 --> 01:06:52,607
JUST GO OVER THERE AND SIT DOWN
AND BE QUIET!

1202
01:06:52,609 --> 01:06:54,442
[ DOG BARKING ]
I HAVE A FUCKING HEADACHE!

1203
01:06:54,444 --> 01:06:57,012
I CAN'T STAND IT.

1204
01:06:57,014 --> 01:06:58,313
I CAN'T STAND IT!

1205
01:06:58,315 --> 01:06:59,581
-HEY.

1206
01:06:59,583 --> 01:07:02,717
[ KATHLEEN SHOUTING
INDISTINCTLY ]

1207
01:07:02,719 --> 01:07:06,454
[ CHILDREN PLAYING, GIGGLING ]

1208
01:07:06,456 --> 01:07:08,790
<i>-...DOUBLE HOMICIDE</i>
<i>OF A YOUNG COUPLE</i>

1209
01:07:08,792 --> 01:07:14,295
CONTINUES TO CREATE CONTROVERSY
MORE THAN A HALF-CENTURY LATER.

1210
01:07:14,297 --> 01:07:16,598
[ <i>DRAMATIC THEME MUSIC PLAYS</i> ]

1211
01:07:20,336 --> 01:07:21,669
[ DOG BARKING ]

1212
01:07:27,376 --> 01:07:30,278
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES,
CHILD BABBLES ]

1213
01:07:30,280 --> 01:07:33,715
<i>-IN THE KLONDIKE,</i>
<i>THE HOFFMAN CREW...</i>

1214
01:07:33,717 --> 01:07:35,383
-WHERE'S MISSY?

1215
01:07:35,385 --> 01:07:36,718
-SLEEPIN'.

1216
01:07:36,720 --> 01:07:38,620
-WHAT ABOUT TOM?

1217
01:07:38,622 --> 01:07:40,488
-WORKIN'.

1218
01:07:40,490 --> 01:07:43,758
-YOU GOT MY MONEY?

1219
01:07:48,731 --> 01:07:50,665
<i>-YOU'RE GETTING THROUGH IT</i>
<i>OVER THERE, DAD.</i>

1220
01:07:50,667 --> 01:07:54,536
[ <i>TV CHATTER</i> ]

1221
01:07:54,538 --> 01:07:57,372
<i>-HOW DID YOU HEAR</i>
<i>ABOUT THE DOUBLE HOMICIDE?</i>

1222
01:07:57,374 --> 01:07:59,741
-SHE GOT FIRED
FROM THE SUNLIGHT JR.

1223
01:07:59,743 --> 01:08:02,577
-THAT FIGURES.

1224
01:08:02,579 --> 01:08:06,314
<i>-...WAY AHEAD OF THE HOFFMAN</i>
<i>TEAM AND THE DAKOTA BOYS.</i>

1225
01:08:06,316 --> 01:08:07,749
<i>-THERE WE GO.</i>

1226
01:08:07,751 --> 01:08:10,218
<i>-SO FAR THIS SEASON,</i>

1227
01:08:10,220 --> 01:08:12,420
<i>HIS WASH PLANT HAS PRODUCED</i>
<i>10 OUNCES OF GOLD,</i>

1228
01:08:12,422 --> 01:08:15,156
<i>WORTH AROUND $16,000.</i>

1229
01:08:18,227 --> 01:08:20,161
-YOU KNOW, YOU GOT HIM
AND HER LIVING HERE.

1230
01:08:20,163 --> 01:08:21,596
I'M GONNA HAVE TO CHARGE YOU
MORE MONEY.

1231
01:08:21,598 --> 01:08:22,864
YOU REALIZE THAT, RIGHT?

1232
01:08:22,866 --> 01:08:24,732
-YOU GOT TO DO
WHAT YOU GOT TO DO.

1233
01:08:26,502 --> 01:08:29,471
-THIS DUDE ROLLING
HIS LITTLE WHEELCHAIR

1234
01:08:29,473 --> 01:08:30,872
ALL OVER THE CARPET.

1235
01:08:30,874 --> 01:08:33,441
IT'S WEAR AND TEAR
ON THE HOUSE.

1236
01:08:33,443 --> 01:08:37,545
-HEY, JUSTIN. NO PROBLEM.
<i>I'LL</i> PAY IT.

1237
01:08:37,547 --> 01:08:39,614
I'M GONNA COME OVER AND PUT ONE
IN YOUR FUCKING HEAD!

1238
01:08:39,616 --> 01:08:41,382
-OH, MY GOD.

1239
01:08:41,384 --> 01:08:43,118
-I'M GONNA PUT ONE
IN YOUR FUCKING HEAD!

1240
01:08:43,120 --> 01:08:44,719
-GET THE FUCK OFF ME!
-MOTHERFUCKER!

1241
01:08:44,721 --> 01:08:47,322
-COME OUT HERE AND CONTROL...
-RICH!

1242
01:08:47,324 --> 01:08:48,590
-...YOUR SILLY ASS BOYFRIEND!

1243
01:08:48,592 --> 01:08:51,226
-RICH! GET OFF!

1244
01:08:51,228 --> 01:08:53,828
RICH!
GET THE FUCK OFF HIM, RICH!

1245
01:08:53,830 --> 01:08:56,231
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

1246
01:08:56,233 --> 01:08:58,299
-YOU'VE BEEN STALKING HER!

1247
01:08:58,301 --> 01:09:00,401
-[ GROANS ]

1248
01:09:00,403 --> 01:09:02,570
-HE'S BEEN STALKING HER.

1249
01:09:02,572 --> 01:09:04,372
-GOOD GRIEF!

1250
01:09:06,842 --> 01:09:10,311
-YEAH.
YOU WANTED TO START SOME SHIT?!

1251
01:09:10,313 --> 01:09:13,214
[ BABY CRYING ]
<i>-IT'S A WHOLE NOTHER BALLGAME.</i>

1252
01:09:13,216 --> 01:09:14,816
-YOU KNOW I GOT THE KEYS
TO THIS HOUSE!

1253
01:09:14,818 --> 01:09:16,551
-YEAH? WHAT'S THAT
SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

1254
01:09:16,553 --> 01:09:19,154
[ BABY CRYING ]

1255
01:09:19,156 --> 01:09:20,655
-THIS IS MY HOUSE!

1256
01:09:22,458 --> 01:09:24,292
-HEY!

1257
01:09:24,294 --> 01:09:27,662
-YOU WANT SOME MORE? HUH?

1258
01:09:29,498 --> 01:09:31,733
-FUCK YOU! FUCK ALL Y'ALL!

1259
01:09:31,735 --> 01:09:33,201
-GO HOME, JUSTIN!

1260
01:09:33,203 --> 01:09:35,703
[ CLATTER ]
-RICHIE BARNES,

1261
01:09:35,705 --> 01:09:37,505
YOU ACT LIKE YOU'RE 10 FEET TALL
AND BULLETPROOF!

1262
01:09:37,507 --> 01:09:39,474
-YEAH, I AM!
-SHIT!

1263
01:09:39,476 --> 01:09:41,743
CODY!

1264
01:09:41,745 --> 01:09:43,745
THERE'S A BIG-ASS MESS
IN THE LIVING ROOM.

1265
01:09:43,747 --> 01:09:45,413
-[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

1266
01:09:45,415 --> 01:09:47,382
<i>-THE FLORIDA LOTTERY</i>
<i>IS CELEBRATING</i>

1267
01:09:47,384 --> 01:09:49,450
<i>OUR 25-YEAR WINNING STREAK</i>
<i>IN A BIG WAY.</i>

1268
01:09:49,452 --> 01:09:50,885
-HEY, PUSSY!

1269
01:09:50,887 --> 01:09:53,555
COME BACK HERE!
I'LL KICK YOUR ASS SOME MORE!

1270
01:09:53,557 --> 01:09:55,523
[ DOG BARKING ]

1271
01:09:55,525 --> 01:09:57,959
-[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

1272
01:10:18,480 --> 01:10:21,916
[ BARKING CONTINUES ]

1273
01:10:21,918 --> 01:10:24,252
[ PEN CLICKS ]

1274
01:10:26,722 --> 01:10:28,856
<i>-EVERY MAKE, EVERY MODEL,</i>
<i>WITH UP TO...</i>

1275
01:10:28,858 --> 01:10:30,892
-YOU SEE THAT?
I GOT HIM GOOD.

1276
01:10:30,894 --> 01:10:33,294
RIGHT IN THE CHOPPERS.

1277
01:10:33,296 --> 01:10:36,631
<i>-AND UP TO $1,500</i>
<i>INSTANT CASH BACK.</i>

1278
01:10:36,633 --> 01:10:39,734
<i>YOU COULD DRIVE AWAY WITH</i>
<i>THE MONEY IN YOUR POCKET.</i>

1279
01:10:39,736 --> 01:10:41,869
-WELL...

1280
01:10:41,871 --> 01:10:46,407
RICH JUST ABOUT CHOKED JUSTIN
TO DEATH OUT THERE.

1281
01:10:46,409 --> 01:10:47,675
[ CHUCKLES ]

1282
01:10:47,677 --> 01:10:49,777
-YOU THINK THAT'S FUNNY?

1283
01:10:49,779 --> 01:10:51,779
-NO. I DON'T THINK IT'S FUNNY.

1284
01:10:51,781 --> 01:10:54,616
I DON'T THINK ANYTHING'S
GODDAMN FUNNY,

1285
01:10:54,618 --> 01:10:57,518
BUT IT'S BETTER THAN CRYING
ALL THE TIME.

1286
01:10:57,520 --> 01:11:00,855
THAT'S WHAT YOU USED TO DO
WHEN YOU WERE A LITTLE GIRL.

1287
01:11:00,857 --> 01:11:02,857
THAT'S ALL YOU WANTED TO DO,
JUST CRY.

1288
01:11:02,859 --> 01:11:04,692
AND NOW LOOK AT YA.

1289
01:11:04,694 --> 01:11:07,662
THERE'S TWO MEN OUT THERE IN
THE KITCHEN FIGHTING OVER YOU,

1290
01:11:07,664 --> 01:11:09,831
AND YOU SHOULD BE HAPPY --
THEY LOVE YOU.

1291
01:11:09,833 --> 01:11:12,467
-THAT AIN'T LOVE.

1292
01:11:12,469 --> 01:11:13,901
-[ Sighing ] WELL...

1293
01:11:13,903 --> 01:11:16,037
RICH DOESN'T HIT YOU.
NEVER HAS.

1294
01:11:16,039 --> 01:11:19,941
SO YOU DID GOOD THERE.

1295
01:11:19,943 --> 01:11:22,577
HEY, YOU WANT A BEER?

1296
01:11:22,579 --> 01:11:26,381
-NO.
I'M FIXING TO EAT.

1297
01:11:26,383 --> 01:11:29,717
[ SIGHS ]

1298
01:11:29,719 --> 01:11:31,986
-EVERY TIME I LOOK AT YOU,

1299
01:11:31,988 --> 01:11:35,590
I SEE MY PRETTY LITTLE GIRL,
MISS.

1300
01:11:35,592 --> 01:11:38,326
SO PRETTY.

1301
01:11:38,328 --> 01:11:41,329
-QUIT DRINKING WHISKEY, MAMA.

1302
01:11:41,331 --> 01:11:43,798
-HEY.

1303
01:11:43,800 --> 01:11:46,868
YOU GONNA MAKE ME
SOME FOOD, TOO?

1304
01:11:46,870 --> 01:11:48,770
-[ SIGHS ]
YEAH, OF COURSE.

1305
01:11:48,772 --> 01:11:49,771
-YOU GOT SOME GOOD ONES.

1306
01:11:49,773 --> 01:11:53,708
-YEP. THAT'S MY RICHIE.

1307
01:11:53,710 --> 01:11:55,743
-JUSTIN LOVES YOU, TOO.

1308
01:11:55,745 --> 01:11:57,745
DON'T YOU FORGET THAT.

1309
01:11:57,747 --> 01:11:59,714
-WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

1310
01:11:59,716 --> 01:12:04,385
-WELL, I'M JUST SAYING THAT,
YOU KNOW, SINCE HIS MAMA PASSED,

1311
01:12:04,387 --> 01:12:06,387
HE'S KIND OF COME TO JESUS

1312
01:12:06,389 --> 01:12:08,456
AND HE'S TAKING BETTER CARE
OF KYLE

1313
01:12:08,458 --> 01:12:10,391
AND HE'S TAKING CARE
OF HIS PROPERTY.

1314
01:12:10,393 --> 01:12:12,493
-YEAH, AND SELLING PILLS
TO JUNKIES.

1315
01:12:12,495 --> 01:12:15,063
-WELL, NO.
I DON'T KNOW NOTHIN' ABOUT THAT.

1316
01:12:15,065 --> 01:12:18,466
-YOU DON'T KNOW NOTHIN'
ABOUT NOTHIN'.

1317
01:12:22,905 --> 01:12:24,906
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

1318
01:12:26,709 --> 01:12:27,775
-MNH.

1319
01:12:27,777 --> 01:12:29,677
[ SIZZLING ]

1320
01:12:29,679 --> 01:12:32,080
-IT'S NICE TO HAVE A REAL STOVE
TO COOK ON.

1321
01:12:32,082 --> 01:12:34,716
AT THE MOTEL,
ALLS I HAD WAS A HOT PLATE.

1322
01:12:34,718 --> 01:12:36,084
YOU KNOW WHAT'S THAT?

1323
01:12:36,086 --> 01:12:38,619
-YEAH, IT'S LIKE, UM,
ONE OF THEM THINGS,

1324
01:12:38,621 --> 01:12:40,822
LIKE A LITTLE TABLE
YOU PLUG IN, RIGHT?

1325
01:12:40,824 --> 01:12:42,423
-THAT'S RIGHT.

1326
01:12:42,425 --> 01:12:44,692
IT'S WHAT YOU USE TO COOK
IN JAIL WITH.

1327
01:12:44,694 --> 01:12:47,028
CAN YOU GET SOME PLATES, HON?

1328
01:12:47,030 --> 01:12:50,665
I WANT TO CHECK
THESE TATER TOTS.

1329
01:12:50,667 --> 01:12:52,767
-I LOVE TATER TOTS.

1330
01:12:52,769 --> 01:12:54,969
-OH, YEAH.
YOU GOT TO EAT THE FISH, TOO.

1331
01:12:54,971 --> 01:12:57,038
THAT'S WHERE YOU GET
YOUR PROTEIN.

1332
01:12:59,074 --> 01:13:01,542
RICH!

1333
01:13:01,544 --> 01:13:04,846
TELL 'EM DINNER'S ALMOST READY.

1334
01:13:04,848 --> 01:13:06,381
[ TRAY CLATTERS ]

1335
01:13:06,383 --> 01:13:07,882
HERE, YOU WANT TO FLIP 'EM?

1336
01:13:07,884 --> 01:13:09,150
-THANK YOU.

1337
01:13:09,152 --> 01:13:10,885
-BE CAREFUL.
IT'S REAL HOT.

1338
01:13:10,887 --> 01:13:12,453
THAT'S IT.

1339
01:13:16,525 --> 01:13:18,626
I MISSED YOU.

1340
01:13:18,628 --> 01:13:20,495
-I MISSED YOU, TOO.

1341
01:13:20,497 --> 01:13:22,964
<i>-HELP CHILDREN IN NEED</i>
<i>BY ATTENDING THE...</i>

1342
01:13:22,966 --> 01:13:26,534
-RICH?!
COME ON! DINNER!

1343
01:13:26,536 --> 01:13:28,936
WILL YOU TELL 'EM?!

1344
01:13:28,938 --> 01:13:32,440
[ <i>DRAMATIC THEME MUSIC PLAYS</i> ]

1345
01:13:32,442 --> 01:13:34,976
-HEY, MEL.
CAN I GET A BEER?

1346
01:13:34,978 --> 01:13:36,911
-NOPE. THERE'S NONE LEFT.

1347
01:13:36,913 --> 01:13:38,112
-ARE YOU SURE?

1348
01:13:38,114 --> 01:13:39,714
-HERE YOU GO.
-YEP.

1349
01:13:39,716 --> 01:13:42,583
-HEY, CODY, CAN YOU GO
RUN OVER TO THE FRIDGE

1350
01:13:42,585 --> 01:13:43,985
AND -- AND CHECK ON MY BEER?

1351
01:13:43,987 --> 01:13:45,453
-[ SIGHS ]

1352
01:13:45,455 --> 01:13:47,422
I DON'T KNOW WHY
YOU DON'T BELIEVE ME.

1353
01:13:47,424 --> 01:13:48,623
I'LL GO.

1354
01:13:48,625 --> 01:13:49,824
SIT DOWN, CODY.

1355
01:13:49,826 --> 01:13:51,659
<i>-83 DEGREES.</i>

1356
01:13:51,661 --> 01:13:54,629
<i>CALL IT PARTLY CLOUDY.</i>
<i>74 RIGHT NOW AT THE AIRPORT.</i>

1357
01:13:54,631 --> 01:13:56,831
-OH, SHIT.

1358
01:13:56,833 --> 01:13:58,766
HOW COME I'M ALWAYS
THE LAST PERSON

1359
01:13:58,768 --> 01:14:00,868
TO KNOW WHEN WE GOT FOLKS
IN THE HOUSE?

1360
01:14:00,870 --> 01:14:04,806
-NO FOLKS -- DAUGHTER.

1361
01:14:04,808 --> 01:14:06,674
-HIM TOO?

1362
01:14:06,676 --> 01:14:09,610
-AH, LEAVE RICHIE BE.
HE'LL KILL YOU IN YOUR SLEEP.

1363
01:14:09,612 --> 01:14:11,078
-GOD DAMN.

1364
01:14:11,080 --> 01:14:13,748
KATHLEEN, I GOT ENOUGH SHIT
TO WORRY ABOUT

1365
01:14:13,750 --> 01:14:16,551
WITHOUT HAVING A HOUSE FULL
OF DAMN VAGRANTS!

1366
01:14:16,553 --> 01:14:17,885
-JUST WAIT ONE MINUTE!

1367
01:14:17,887 --> 01:14:19,554
-WAIT FOR WHAT?
-YOU COME IN HERE --

1368
01:14:19,556 --> 01:14:21,055
-I COME IN HERE, YEAH.

1369
01:14:21,057 --> 01:14:22,690
-WE HAVE BEEN HERE
ALL AFTERNOON COOKING!

1370
01:14:22,692 --> 01:14:24,192
-I DON'T NEED ALL THESE PEOPLE
IN HERE!

1371
01:14:24,194 --> 01:14:25,960
-YOU WOULDN'T BELIEVE
THE AMOUNT OF EFFORT

1372
01:14:25,962 --> 01:14:27,695
THAT WENT INTO DOING THIS MEAL!

1373
01:14:27,697 --> 01:14:29,764
[ DOOR SLAMS ]
-IT'S MAMA'S WHISKEY.

1374
01:14:29,766 --> 01:14:31,098
DON'T TELL HER
I SWIPED SOME FOR YA.

1375
01:14:31,100 --> 01:14:33,034
-OH. THANKS, BABE.

1376
01:14:33,036 --> 01:14:36,137
-YES, THEY HAVE TO STAY!
-[ SLURPS ]

1377
01:14:36,139 --> 01:14:38,039
-THERE YOU GO, CODY.
-THANK YOU.

1378
01:14:38,041 --> 01:14:39,740
-HEY, BABE?
-WHAT?

1379
01:14:39,742 --> 01:14:42,910
-I NOTICE THIS ONE NEEDS
A LITTLE HELP WITH HER FOOD.

1380
01:14:42,912 --> 01:14:44,612
-THAT'S CHLOE.

1381
01:14:44,614 --> 01:14:46,714
-I KNOW WHO CHLOE IS.

1382
01:14:46,716 --> 01:14:48,182
-[ SIGHS ]
CHLOE, COME HERE.

1383
01:14:48,184 --> 01:14:50,685
YOU GONNA HAVE SOME FISH?

1384
01:14:50,687 --> 01:14:52,019
COME ON. YOU SAID YOU WOULD.

1385
01:14:52,021 --> 01:14:54,021
-[ BABBLES ]

1386
01:14:54,023 --> 01:14:55,256
I DONE.

1387
01:14:55,258 --> 01:14:56,757
-YOU'RE ALL DONE?

1388
01:14:56,759 --> 01:14:58,493
WELL, LET'S HAVE
A LITTLE BIT MORE.

1389
01:14:58,495 --> 01:15:01,596
GOT TO EAT SOMETHING.
CHLOE? COME ON.

1390
01:15:01,598 --> 01:15:05,233
[ KATHLEEN AND TOM ARGUING
IN NEXT ROOM ]

1391
01:15:05,235 --> 01:15:06,634
-I'M NOT HUNGRY.

1392
01:15:06,636 --> 01:15:08,269
-WHAT? [ SIGHS ]

1393
01:15:08,271 --> 01:15:11,072
-KATHLEEN ALWAYS TRIES TO GET
HIM TO EAT <i>OUR</i> FOOD,

1394
01:15:11,074 --> 01:15:12,607
BUT HE DON'T EVER WANNA.

1395
01:15:12,609 --> 01:15:14,709
-[ SIGHS ] WELL, YOU WANT
SOME MORE KETCHUP?

1396
01:15:14,711 --> 01:15:16,644
SEE, IF YOU PUT A LOT
OF KETCHUP ON IT,

1397
01:15:16,646 --> 01:15:17,845
YOU WON'T TASTE NOTHING
BUT KETCHUP.

1398
01:15:17,847 --> 01:15:19,146
IT'S REAL SWEET.

1399
01:15:19,148 --> 01:15:21,749
-HE SHOULD GO LIVE
WITH SOME MEXICANS.

1400
01:15:21,751 --> 01:15:25,119
-[ SIGHS ]
JUST TRY EATING SOME.

1401
01:15:25,121 --> 01:15:27,121
-I'M NOT HUNGRY.

1402
01:15:27,123 --> 01:15:28,523
-WELL, ALL RIGHT.

1403
01:15:28,525 --> 01:15:31,092
GO ON AND PUT IT
IN THE KITCHEN YOURSELF.

1404
01:15:31,094 --> 01:15:34,061
WAIT. WHAT'S THAT?

1405
01:15:34,063 --> 01:15:35,963
[ TV CHATTER ]

1406
01:15:35,965 --> 01:15:38,165
YOU GOT BEDBUGS HERE?

1407
01:15:38,167 --> 01:15:40,801
-I -- I DON'T KNOW.

1408
01:15:40,803 --> 01:15:44,071
-YEP.

1409
01:15:44,073 --> 01:15:46,073
IT'S BEDBUGS.

1410
01:15:46,075 --> 01:15:49,076
LOOK AT HIS LEGS.
IT'S ON HIS BACK, EVERYWHERE.

1411
01:15:49,078 --> 01:15:53,147
[ ARGUING CONTINUES ]

1412
01:15:53,149 --> 01:15:54,549
-HEY, CODY?
TURN UP THE TV, WOULD YOU?

1413
01:15:54,551 --> 01:15:56,717
-WHY DON'T <i>YOU?</i>

1414
01:15:56,719 --> 01:15:59,720
-WHAT, DO I GOT TO ASK TWICE?!

1415
01:15:59,722 --> 01:16:01,989
TURN UP THE TV!

1416
01:16:04,860 --> 01:16:07,228
-[ Louder ] <i>THE FRIDAY NIGHT</i>
<i>BLITZ TONIGHT</i>

1417
01:16:07,230 --> 01:16:09,564
<i>AT 11:15</i>
<i>ONLY ON NEWS CHANNEL 8.</i>

1418
01:16:09,566 --> 01:16:11,065
<i>-STORM TEAM 8 WEATHER MAX.</i>

1419
01:16:11,067 --> 01:16:13,801
-WHAT IS WITH THE ATTITUDE
I'M GETTING HERE?

1420
01:16:13,803 --> 01:16:15,136
<i>-DOWNLOAD IT FOR FREE.</i>

1421
01:16:15,138 --> 01:16:16,337
<i>-EARLIER THIS WEEK,</i>

1422
01:16:16,339 --> 01:16:18,272
<i>RESIDENTS LIVING</i>
<i>AT THE SANTOMICO</i>

1423
01:16:18,274 --> 01:16:21,242
<i>APARTMENT COMPLEX IN TAMPA</i>
<i>CALLED 8 NEWS ON YOUR SIDE</i>

1424
01:16:21,244 --> 01:16:24,178
<i>LOOKING FOR SOME HELP</i>
<i>AFTER FINDING BATS EVERYWHERE.</i>

1425
01:16:24,180 --> 01:16:26,581
<i>THE CREATURES HAD INFESTED</i>
<i>SEVERAL BUILDINGS.</i>

1426
01:16:26,583 --> 01:16:28,649
-COME ON. SIT UP HERE.

1427
01:16:28,651 --> 01:16:30,217
COME ON.

1428
01:16:30,219 --> 01:16:32,219
[ SIGHS ]

1429
01:16:32,221 --> 01:16:34,121
<i>-YESTERDAY, TRAPPERS FROM WILD</i>
<i>LIFE SOLUTIONS SHOWED UP TO...</i>

1430
01:16:34,123 --> 01:16:36,891
-MEL?

1431
01:16:36,893 --> 01:16:38,659
MEL?

1432
01:16:38,661 --> 01:16:40,061
-WHAT?

1433
01:16:40,063 --> 01:16:43,164
-YOU'RE GONNA MAKE
A BEAUTIFUL MOTHER.

1434
01:16:43,166 --> 01:16:48,235
-WELL, I CAN'T HAVE YOU DRINKING
LIKE YOU DID TODAY, RICH.

1435
01:16:48,237 --> 01:16:50,037
NO, SIR.

1436
01:16:50,039 --> 01:16:52,106
NOT YOU AND MY MOM DRINKING
ALL FUCKING DAY LONG.

1437
01:16:52,108 --> 01:16:54,709
-BABE? BABE. BABE.
CALM DOWN.

1438
01:16:54,711 --> 01:16:56,377
YOU KNOW, THIS HAS BEEN
A TOUGH WEEK FOR BOTH OF US.

1439
01:16:56,379 --> 01:16:58,145
BUT REMEMBER.

1440
01:16:58,147 --> 01:17:01,282
WE GOT A PLAN, AND WE'RE TAKING
CARE OF OUR BUSINESS.

1441
01:17:01,284 --> 01:17:04,685
AND, NO, I DON'T INTEND
TO KEEP ON DRINKING LIKE THIS.

1442
01:17:04,687 --> 01:17:07,922
BUT IT'S BEEN, UH...
IT'S BEEN STRESSFUL, YOU KNOW?

1443
01:17:07,924 --> 01:17:12,860
-[ SCOFFS ]
POOR YOU. "STRESSFUL."

1444
01:17:12,862 --> 01:17:15,663
<i>THAT'S</i> STRESSFUL?

1445
01:17:15,665 --> 01:17:19,200
HOW ABOUT WORKING A JOB?
HOW DO YOU THINK <i>THAT</i> FEELS?

1446
01:17:19,202 --> 01:17:22,670
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.
I AIN'T WORKING A JOB,

1447
01:17:22,672 --> 01:17:26,273
TAKING CARE OF NO DRUNK,
AND PLUS A BABY ON TOP OF THAT.

1448
01:17:26,275 --> 01:17:29,010
FUCK THAT SHIT!
WHO'S GONNA TAKE CARE OF ME?

1449
01:17:29,012 --> 01:17:31,312
-I'M GONNA TAKE CARE OF YOU.

1450
01:17:31,314 --> 01:17:33,848
I TOLD YOU THAT.
-HOW ARE YOU GONNA DO THAT

1451
01:17:33,850 --> 01:17:35,783
STUCK IN THAT THING
ALL FUCKING DAY LONG?!

1452
01:17:35,785 --> 01:17:37,785
YOU CAN'T HARDLY TAKE CARE
OF YOURSELF!

1453
01:17:37,787 --> 01:17:39,387
OH, ACT LIKE
YOU GOT SOME BRAINS!

1454
01:17:39,389 --> 01:17:40,921
QUIT IT, RICH!

1455
01:17:40,923 --> 01:17:42,156
YOU'RE GONNA WRECK
THE ONLY THING WE OWN!

1456
01:17:42,158 --> 01:17:43,724
-I TOLD YOU
I'D TAKE CARE OF YOU!

1457
01:17:43,726 --> 01:17:45,126
-WELL, PUT YOUR MONEY
WHERE YOUR MOUTH IS,

1458
01:17:45,128 --> 01:17:47,228
'CAUSE I DON'T
FUCKING BELIEVE YOU!

1459
01:17:47,230 --> 01:17:49,230
[ DOG BARKING ]

1460
01:17:51,667 --> 01:17:55,903
WHAT ARE YOU DOI-- [SIGHS]

1461
01:17:55,905 --> 01:17:57,204
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

1462
01:17:57,206 --> 01:17:58,439
WE'VE GOT NOWHERE ELSE
TO SLEEP, RICH!

1463
01:17:58,441 --> 01:18:01,375
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

1464
01:18:01,377 --> 01:18:03,210
OH, I SEE.

1465
01:18:03,212 --> 01:18:08,082
SO, WHAT, YOU'RE JUST GONNA
TAKE OFF, IS THAT IT?

1466
01:18:08,084 --> 01:18:09,984
[ CLATTERING LIGHTLY ]

1467
01:18:09,986 --> 01:18:12,286
RICH.

1468
01:18:12,288 --> 01:18:14,755
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER, REVS ]

1469
01:18:14,757 --> 01:18:17,358
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]

1470
01:19:06,007 --> 01:19:08,209
[ ZIPPER ZIPS ]

1471
01:19:11,446 --> 01:19:13,814
[ DOG BARKS ]

1472
01:19:13,816 --> 01:19:16,083
-WHO IS IT?

1473
01:19:16,085 --> 01:19:18,385
-MISSY.

1474
01:19:20,455 --> 01:19:22,022
[ DOG BARKS ]

1475
01:19:22,024 --> 01:19:24,425
-SHH, SHH.

1476
01:19:27,496 --> 01:19:29,296
-IS KRYSTAL HERE?

1477
01:19:29,298 --> 01:19:32,466
-YOU ABOUT LOST YOUR MIND.
NO.

1478
01:19:32,468 --> 01:19:34,769
KYLE'S ASLEEP, THOUGH.
KEEP YOUR VOICE DOWN.

1479
01:19:34,771 --> 01:19:35,903
[ DOG BARKS ]

1480
01:19:35,905 --> 01:19:36,971
SHH.

1481
01:19:39,007 --> 01:19:40,775
-HOW'S HE?

1482
01:19:40,777 --> 01:19:42,309
-HOW'S WHO?

1483
01:19:42,311 --> 01:19:46,213
-KYLE, DUMB ASS.

1484
01:19:48,116 --> 01:19:50,084
-YOU COME TO APOLOGIZE?

1485
01:19:50,086 --> 01:19:51,519
-TO WHO?

1486
01:19:51,521 --> 01:19:54,321
-TO <i>ME.</i>

1487
01:19:54,323 --> 01:19:57,258
-MAYBE.

1488
01:20:02,464 --> 01:20:07,968
LOOK, I -- I'M NOT GONNA BEAT
AROUND THE BUSH.

1489
01:20:07,970 --> 01:20:10,504
I NEED SOMETHING.

1490
01:20:10,506 --> 01:20:14,241
-[ SCOFFS ] BABY, I THOUGHT
YOU HAD EVERYTHING.

1491
01:20:14,243 --> 01:20:17,111
WHAT DO YOU WANT -- MONEY?

1492
01:20:17,113 --> 01:20:18,579
-YEAH.

1493
01:20:22,984 --> 01:20:25,019
-HAVE A SEAT.

1494
01:20:37,165 --> 01:20:38,432
WELL?

1495
01:20:43,839 --> 01:20:46,173
-RICHIE GOT ME PREGNANT.

1496
01:20:47,576 --> 01:20:50,377
I NEED HELP.

1497
01:20:50,379 --> 01:20:52,947
-WHY DON'T YOU ASK RICHIE
FOR HELP, THEN?

1498
01:20:52,949 --> 01:20:57,952
WHAT KIND OF MAN IS HE?!

1499
01:20:57,954 --> 01:20:59,386
-HE'S GONE.

1500
01:20:59,388 --> 01:21:02,423
I DON'T KNOW WHERE HE'S AT,

1501
01:21:02,425 --> 01:21:05,259
BUT I GOT TO GET OUT
OF MY MAMA'S HOUSE.

1502
01:21:05,261 --> 01:21:07,494
AND, PLUS, YOU OWE ME.

1503
01:21:10,165 --> 01:21:13,534
-YOU ARE TRASH!
YOU KNOW THAT?!

1504
01:21:13,536 --> 01:21:17,471
EVER SINCE YOU STARTED GOING OUT
WITH THAT CRIPPLE,

1505
01:21:17,473 --> 01:21:19,940
YOU ACT ALL STUCK UP!

1506
01:21:19,942 --> 01:21:22,309
REAL STUCK UP!

1507
01:21:22,311 --> 01:21:25,546
I'M FUCKING SICK OF IT!

1508
01:21:25,548 --> 01:21:30,084
WHO THE FUCK
DO YOU THINK YOU ARE?!

1509
01:21:31,653 --> 01:21:33,254
-HI, KYLE.

1510
01:21:33,256 --> 01:21:35,389
-HEY, MISSY.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

1511
01:21:35,391 --> 01:21:37,157
-GO BACK TO BED!

1512
01:21:41,363 --> 01:21:44,331
AND YOU -- YOU GET THE FUCK OUT
OF MY HOUSE!

1513
01:21:47,602 --> 01:21:50,938
-I AIN'T LEAVING
TILL YOU GIVE ME SOME CASH.

1514
01:21:50,940 --> 01:21:55,109
-GET THE FUCK OUT OF MY HOUSE!
GET UP!

1515
01:21:55,111 --> 01:21:57,478
GO! BEFORE IT GETS WORSE!

1516
01:21:57,480 --> 01:21:59,546
GET THE FUCK OUT OF MY HOUSE!

1517
01:21:59,548 --> 01:22:02,449
[ DOG BARKS ]

1518
01:22:02,451 --> 01:22:06,020
-MISSY! COME BACK.

1519
01:22:07,656 --> 01:22:11,125
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS,
BIRDS CHIRP ]

1520
01:22:28,076 --> 01:22:31,078
-[ Echoing ] I NEED TO KNOW
IF YOU'RE 100% SURE

1521
01:22:31,080 --> 01:22:34,481
YOU WANT TO TERMINATE
THIS PREGNANCY.

1522
01:22:34,483 --> 01:22:37,217
-YES, MA'AM.

1523
01:22:37,219 --> 01:22:40,621
-DO YOU HAVE A PARTNER?

1524
01:22:40,623 --> 01:22:43,157
-NO.

1525
01:22:43,159 --> 01:22:46,226
-HAVE YOU TOLD ANYONE
ABOUT YOUR DECISION TODAY?

1526
01:22:48,697 --> 01:22:51,365
-NO.

1527
01:22:51,367 --> 01:22:53,667
-YOU OKAY WITH THAT?

1528
01:22:53,669 --> 01:22:55,602
-MM-HMM.

1529
01:22:57,472 --> 01:23:00,607
[ LIGHT WHIRRING AND HISSING ]

1530
01:23:21,329 --> 01:23:24,598
-OKAY. WE'RE DONE.

1531
01:23:26,634 --> 01:23:28,135
[ GLOVE SNAPS ]

1532
01:23:28,137 --> 01:23:30,170
YOU DID REAL GOOD.

1533
01:23:30,172 --> 01:23:32,740
JUST TAKE A MINUTE, RELAX.
THE NURSE WILL TAKE CARE OF YOU.

1534
01:23:32,742 --> 01:23:34,541
-THANKS.

1535
01:23:40,248 --> 01:23:42,483
[ SIGHS ]

1536
01:23:43,718 --> 01:23:45,252
-HI, HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

1537
01:23:45,254 --> 01:23:47,588
YEAH, THEY SAY EVERYTHING
WENT REALLY WELL.

1538
01:23:47,590 --> 01:23:50,257
UM, I JUST HAVE SOME MORE
INFORMATION FOR YOU.

1539
01:23:50,259 --> 01:23:51,725
I NEED YOU TO, UM,

1540
01:23:51,727 --> 01:23:54,061
CHECK YOUR TEMPERATURE FOR US
FOR THE NEXT WEEK,

1541
01:23:54,063 --> 01:23:56,463
ONCE IN THE MORNING
AND ONCE IN THE EVENING.

1542
01:23:56,465 --> 01:23:58,298
IF IT EVER GETS ABOVE 100.4,

1543
01:23:58,300 --> 01:24:00,801
I NEED YOU TO CALL US
IMMEDIATELY, OKAY?

1544
01:24:00,803 --> 01:24:04,038
IT'S REALLY IMPORTANT
TO COME BACK IN TWO WEEKS

1545
01:24:04,040 --> 01:24:05,439
FOR YOUR PELVIC EXAM.

1546
01:24:07,409 --> 01:24:10,511
OKAY, NOW, YOU'VE BEEN GIVEN
PRESCRIPTION MEDICATION --

1547
01:24:10,513 --> 01:24:13,047
-EXCUSE ME.
CAN -- CAN I GET A DOUGHNUT?

1548
01:24:13,049 --> 01:24:14,515
-OH.

1549
01:24:16,317 --> 01:24:17,618
-THANKS.

1550
01:24:17,620 --> 01:24:19,053
-MM-HMM.

1551
01:24:19,055 --> 01:24:21,321
UH, OKAY.

1552
01:24:21,323 --> 01:24:23,590
YOU'VE BEEN GIVEN PRESCRIPTION
MEDICATION, TWO TYPES.

1553
01:24:23,592 --> 01:24:25,292
ONE IS TO PREVENT INFECTION,

1554
01:24:25,294 --> 01:24:27,828
AND THE OTHER ONE ENCOURAGES
THE UTERUS TO CONTRACT

1555
01:24:27,830 --> 01:24:29,430
AND HELPS MINIMIZE BLEEDING.

1556
01:24:29,432 --> 01:24:31,432
UM, SOMETIMES...

1557
01:24:48,583 --> 01:24:51,418
[ CHATTER ]

1558
01:25:20,782 --> 01:25:23,383
-PUT IT BACK.

1559
01:25:23,385 --> 01:25:24,818
-WHERE DOES THIS GO?

1560
01:25:24,820 --> 01:25:26,353
-I KNOW WHERE IT GOES.

1561
01:25:26,355 --> 01:25:27,721
-I DO TOO.

1562
01:25:27,723 --> 01:25:31,725
-BUBBA, WHERE DOES --
DOES <i>THIS</i> GO?

1563
01:25:31,727 --> 01:25:33,861
-UH, WE DON'T NEED IT.

1564
01:25:36,564 --> 01:25:39,333
-HEY, MISSY.
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

1565
01:25:39,335 --> 01:25:42,503
-MY CAR.

1566
01:25:42,505 --> 01:25:44,338
-I HAD A LONG NIGHT.

1567
01:25:44,340 --> 01:25:46,340
I GOT TO GET SOME SLEEP.

1568
01:25:46,342 --> 01:25:48,175
-NO. NO. NO. NO.
YOU CAN'T GO BACK THERE.

1569
01:25:48,177 --> 01:25:50,878
TOM CAME IN IN THE MIDDLE
OF THE NIGHT LAST NIGHT

1570
01:25:50,880 --> 01:25:53,380
stoned out of his mind.

1571
01:25:53,382 --> 01:25:54,848
AND I KNOW.

1572
01:25:54,850 --> 01:25:56,817
HE SAID HE WAS GONNA QUIT,
BUT [SCOFFS]

1573
01:25:56,819 --> 01:26:00,454
ANYWAY, YOU WOULDN'T BELIEVE
THE NIGHT I'VE HAD.

1574
01:26:00,456 --> 01:26:03,323
[ Straining ] OH.

1575
01:26:03,325 --> 01:26:04,658
[ SIGHS ]

1576
01:26:06,761 --> 01:26:09,563
WHY THE LONG FACE, MISSY?

1577
01:26:09,565 --> 01:26:12,199
WELL, YOU KNOW, NORA DECIDED

1578
01:26:12,201 --> 01:26:16,370
SHE WAS GONNA HAVE NIGHTMARES
ALL NIGHT LONG.

1579
01:26:16,372 --> 01:26:18,605
AND SHE WAS CRYING
AND SHE WAS YELLING.

1580
01:26:18,607 --> 01:26:21,475
THEN CHLOE WOKE UP THROWING UP
ALL OVER THE PLACE.

1581
01:26:21,477 --> 01:26:24,745
AND THEN YOU NEVER GET CODY UP
IN TIME TO HELP WITH ANYBODY.

1582
01:26:24,747 --> 01:26:26,480
AND ON TOP OF ALL THAT,

1583
01:26:26,482 --> 01:26:29,550
I MEAN, WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH YOU AND RICH?

1584
01:26:29,552 --> 01:26:32,953
I MEAN, HE'S BEEN SITTING OUT
THERE ALL DAY LONG.

1585
01:26:32,955 --> 01:26:35,689
[ CHILDREN BABBLING ]

1586
01:27:14,395 --> 01:27:16,530
[ MOTORCYCLE ENGINE REVS
IN DISTANCE ]

1587
01:27:42,724 --> 01:27:46,360
-[ SIGHS ]
I HAD TO DO IT.

1588
01:27:46,362 --> 01:27:49,529
-[ SIGHS ]

1589
01:27:49,531 --> 01:27:52,466
-I'M SORRY.

1590
01:27:55,637 --> 01:27:59,339
WE CAN'T HAVE NO BABY, RICH.

1591
01:28:01,409 --> 01:28:04,044
-I KNEW YOU WERE THINKING IT.

1592
01:28:07,782 --> 01:28:09,950
I KNEW IT.

1593
01:28:15,923 --> 01:28:18,025
WHAT ABOUT US?

1594
01:28:32,907 --> 01:28:35,575
I WANT TO BE WITH YOU.

1595
01:28:38,379 --> 01:28:40,814
I STILL DO.

1596
01:28:46,521 --> 01:28:48,822
-[ Voice breaking ] FOR REAL?

1597
01:29:13,414 --> 01:29:16,116
[ Sighing ] OH, RICH.

1598
01:29:26,728 --> 01:29:29,029
YOU'RE NOT MAD AT ME?

1599
01:29:31,032 --> 01:29:33,567
-NO.

1600
01:29:33,569 --> 01:29:35,402
I'M NOT.

1601
01:29:37,972 --> 01:29:40,741
[ SIGHS ]

1602
01:29:40,743 --> 01:29:42,609
-[ SIGHS ]

1603
01:29:47,448 --> 01:29:49,916
IT WAS HARD, RICH.

1604
01:29:52,687 --> 01:29:54,855
-YEAH.

1605
01:30:00,661 --> 01:30:04,030
-I ATE A WHOLE BAG
OF DOUGHNUTS.

1606
01:30:05,733 --> 01:30:07,601
-THAT'S GOOD.

1607
01:30:10,772 --> 01:30:13,774
THAT'S GOOD.

1608
01:30:13,776 --> 01:30:16,777
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]

